snippet.title: Response to rebel wisdom's comics and superheros; Jordan Greenhall and Akira the Don.
snippet.description:
2018-12-26  response to this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s6KSJqMI0NU

My response focuses on core belief's and some philosophical (/spiritual) points of contention.. please try get through it, it only rejoins into more direct commentary near the end... I'm sorry that it takes about 30mins before the recording starts to collect some cohesive traction. 

I still feel I need to modify my views in being more permissive of Jordan Greenhall's contribution in some particular fashion, I think in some sort of metaphysical pundit dialog, he may produce more intellectual value.
